detaileddescription.para: Whether the buffer, if it represents a valid descriptor, contains a derivation path deeper than a given maximum depth. Note this may also be hit for deriv paths in origins.

detaileddescription.para: Whether the buffer, if it represents a valid descriptor, contains a fragment with more sub-fragments than the given maximum.
Whether the buffer, if it represents a valid descriptor, contains a fragment with more wrappers than the given maximum.
